      <title>油漆制造商阿克苏诺贝尔将削减 2,000 个工作岗位以削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/paintmaker-akzo-nobel-to-slash-2-000-jobs-in-cost-cutting-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲最大的涂料制造商阿克苏诺贝尔 (Akzo Nobel NV) 表示，将在明年年底前裁员 2,000 人，以提高盈利能力并降低成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/paintmaker-akzo-nobel-to-slash-2-000-jobs-in-cost-cutting-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰资产管理推出资产净值融资策略，目标金额达 10 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/hsbc-am-launches-nav-financing-strategy-with-1-billion-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司的资产管理部门推出了一只基金，帮助私募股权公司以其投资组合为抵押借款，这是该行作为其另类信贷业务扩张的一部分首次推出此类基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/hsbc-am-launches-nav-financing-strategy-with-1-billion-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美今年第二次利用债券市场发行美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/aramco-taps-debt-markets-for-second-dollar-bond-sale-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯国有石油巨头在筹集 60 亿美元资金仅两个月后就开始发售第二轮国际债券，这是该国今年债务狂潮中的最新一笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/aramco-taps-debt-markets-for-second-dollar-bond-sale-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EQT 集团的 Salata 谈印度战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/eqt-group-s-salata-on-india-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EQT 集团亚洲区主席兼亚洲私人信贷业务主管 Jean Eric Salata 讨论了印度私募股权市场的投资机会。他在《彭博市场亚洲》节目中独家采访了 Haslinda Amin。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/eqt-group-s-salata-on-india-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:59:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>房地产市场回暖之际，房东 SBB 计划进行住房部门 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/landlord-sbb-plans-housing-unit-ipo-as-real-estate-market-thaws</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典房地产开发商 SBB 将公开出售其住宅部门 Sveafastigheter AB 高达 49% 的股份，这是该国房地产资金紧缩局面开始缓解的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/landlord-sbb-plans-housing-unit-ipo-as-real-estate-market-thaws</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:54:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的 Gori 谈中国刺激计划和印度扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/jpmorgan-s-gori-on-china-stimulus-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通欧洲、中东和非洲地区首席执行官兼全球银行业务联席主管 Filippo Gori 表示，从长远来看，恢复消费者信心对中国更为重要。他在摩根大通印度投资者峰会期间与 Haslinda Amin 和 Menaka Doshi 进行了“彭博市场亚洲”访谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/jpmorgan-s-gori-on-china-stimulus-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑设立股票稳定基金，中国人民银行释放 1130 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-to-allow-funds-brokers-to-tap-pboc-funding-to-buy-stocks-m1frm2al</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在考虑设立股票稳定基金，并将向陷入困境的股市提供至少 8000 亿元人民币（1130 亿美元）的初始流动性支持。内地和香港股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-to-allow-funds-brokers-to-tap-pboc-funding-to-buy-stocks-m1frm2al</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:36:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北京采取一系列措施刺激经济，铁矿石价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iron-ore-spikes-as-beijing-takes-slew-of-steps-to-aid-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国宣布一系列重大措施促进增长和支撑陷入困境的房地产市场之后，大宗商品价格上涨，铁矿石价格飙升，铜价升至 7 月份以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iron-ore-spikes-as-beijing-takes-slew-of-steps-to-aid-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员纷纷涌向股市，中国国债回吐涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-s-10-year-bond-yield-falls-to-2-for-first-time-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国央行大规模刺激计划推动看涨投资者撤离债券市场、转向股票市场之后，中国基准债券收益率从历史低点反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-s-10-year-bond-yield-falls-to-2-for-first-time-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:18:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国宣布全面支持措施后油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府出台一系列经济政策支持措施，以及以色列对黎巴嫩真主党目标进行大规模袭击导致中东局势持续紧张，导致油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 23:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
